            <description><![CDATA[【孩子摔倒颅内出血，奶奶：“能不能不拍片，不做检查？”】在儿童安全事故里，意外跌落造成的大概占30%，平均年龄只有5岁。6岁的笔笔是其中一个，从沙发掉下，家长没有重视，直接变成脑疝，需要做开颅手术。而奶奶担心辐射，不让给孩子拍片，医生强硬表态：必须要拍！被家长耽误的时间，只能由医生抢回来。15分钟，还不够来把游戏，儿科医生却做完了开颅手术！《闪闪的儿科医生》第二集精彩继续👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E5%84%BF%E5%8C%BB%E9%A6%96%E6%92%AD%E7%BD%91%E5%8F%8B%E7%9B%B4%E5%91%BC%E9%A3%99%E6%B3%AA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E5%84%BF%E5%8C%BB%E9%A6%96%E6%92%AD%E7%BD%91%E5%8F%8B%E7%9B%B4%E5%91%BC%E9%A3%99%E6%B3%AA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#闪闪儿医首播网友直呼飙泪#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#闪闪的儿科医生#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4899586779840551" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hdsevmttz2j21hc0u0n81.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/lOc876olgx085jeVmHWg01041200ClYT0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BVp4ysnknHVZu&amp;Expires=1683666958&amp;ssig=tMWdbmrLI6&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/xiE9XCe6gx085jeUriuY01041200ku0j0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BVp4ysnknHVZu&amp;Expires=1683666958&amp;ssig=np7o1YFYhC&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/hxfxyPelgx085jeTOXv201041200dhy50E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BVp4ysnknHVZu&amp;Expires=16836